{"tid":1049731,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"宇宙少女舞台上被男舞者「鹹豬手摸胸」粉絲氣炸...男舞者的回應更是讓人傻眼！","createTime":"2019-03-06T13:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T01:59:47.000Z","uid":46435,"like":320,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"be1e282b0cbf89cb0cb908ad269bdf37a8b9b72a","tid":1049731,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:10:28.000Z","msg":"3月2-3日兩天是宇宙少女第一次單獨演唱會，演唱會不只展現了三年來的成長，也有展現各成員魅力的cover舞台。Luda表演了宣美的《24 hours》讓現場粉絲又驚又喜，但卻在表演中發生了爭議。《24 hours》表演途中，有名男舞者摸了成員Luda的胸，而在SNS成為了爭議話題！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JuRwtBh5qxM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJuRwtBh5qxM&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=102f2d30\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JuRwtBh5qxM</a><br />\n在表演的2分09秒，可以看到男舞者扶著Luda，而要將Luda往下倒的動作則是直接摸到了胸部，讓台下粉絲相當慌張！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/1SvnMsBMhH7Y7D1Ern/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F1SvnMsBMhH7Y7D1Ern%2Fgiphy.gif&h=10d19c25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飯拍影片傳出讓更多人看到男舞者的惡行，不只粉絲生氣，路人也相當傻眼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4bdp9-Qa7BQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4bdp9-Qa7BQ&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=f02df749\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4bdp9-Qa7BQ</a><br />\n但隔一天的表演，同樣的動作，男舞者並沒有摸到Luda的胸，因此更明顯的是前一天表演男舞者的失誤。<br />\n<br />\n甚至演唱會結束後，男舞者的IG還是演唱會的後記，寫著從成員練習生時期看到現在，開演唱會的樣子讓人感動，還寫著&quot;最後照片的意義是只有我們知道的秘密ㅋㅋ&quot;，造成更大的爭議！<br />\n<br />\n粉絲剛開始還以為只是男舞者的失誤，已經很生氣的情況，男舞者還嬉皮笑臉的發文，讓人更憤怒。知道男舞者最後照片意義的人，還留言嬉笑，寫著#手。<br />\n<br />\n男舞者不但沒任何道歉，還嬉笑的以這個事件為嘲弄的點，讓爭議越演越烈，男舞者也將IG設為私人，粉絲也紛紛向公司要求回應，希望公司儘快發聲明啊！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個男dancer都幾能狼死下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16039d072efc4204c59d3aa75f8b12920f936dcc","tid":1049731,"uid":25560,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:11:44.000Z","msg":"小意思"},{"pid":"4db7cc3b2d7a3e1386d772cb44b28c48d612bba8","tid":1049731,"uid":74065,"like":323,"dislike":20,"score":303,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:18:51.000Z","msg":"COUPLE黎<br />\n好似泫雅咁調情"},{"pid":"97d11b9ad51eb41c8f48b64c5ea6f9ba7b132515","tid":1049731,"uid":43061,"like":124,"dislike":13,"score":111,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:22:36.000Z","msg":"呢下真係過份左"},{"pid":"28464505c20de7218cb902328cddbbfc7e398295","tid":1049731,"uid":3189,"like":583,"dislike":21,"score":562,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:22:54.000Z","msg":"女idol啲胸三分二都係墊嚟<br />\n是但啦"},{"pid":"0d96e47c2fa4beb541e4aa88b905bbbc110f21f4","tid":1049731,"uid":131980,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:24:20.000Z","msg":"蜻蜓點水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dda9deef9ac248538bebda97e4cd60e3d04decb","tid":1049731,"uid":181527,"like":228,"dislike":1,"score":227,"quote":{"pid":"28464505c20de7218cb902328cddbbfc7e398295","tid":1049731,"uid":3189,"like":583,"dislike":21,"score":562,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:22:54.000Z","msg":"女idol啲胸三分二都係墊嚟<br />\n是但啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:28:43.000Z","msg":"只有我們知道的秘密<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169bfaa09093017940109d6352d115987cc5cdae","tid":1049731,"uid":46435,"like":89,"dislike":0,"score":89,"quote":{"pid":"4db7cc3b2d7a3e1386d772cb44b28c48d612bba8","tid":1049731,"uid":74065,"like":323,"dislike":20,"score":303,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:18:51.000Z","msg":"COUPLE黎<br />\n好似泫雅咁調情"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:30:39.000Z","msg":"咁應該要拎對波去撞個男dancer"},{"pid":"e1f0d3599bfaa9f32a4b05c235700544f6de700d","tid":1049731,"uid":17232,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"28464505c20de7218cb902328cddbbfc7e398295","tid":1049731,"uid":3189,"like":58